    "properties_description": "The main therapeutic properties of Linosyris diffusa are anti-inflammatory and antimicrobial activities. Antioxidant properties in this plant help to neutralize free radicals and protect against oxidative stress, which is responsible for various diseases. The anti-inflammatory properties of Linosyris diffusa may contribute to its potential in treating inflammatory conditions, such as arthritis and other rheumatologic disorders. The antimicrobial properties of this plant are attributed to the presence of flavonoids and saponins, which are known to exhibit antibacterial and antifungal activities. The plant's sedative and anxiolytic properties may also be beneficial in managing anxiety and insomnia.",
